# Documentation Contributor Guide

## Overview

Documentation site built with **Mintlify**. Lives in `docs/` directory.

## Directory Structure

**CRITICAL RULE**: Directory structure MUST mirror the navigation structure in `docs.json`.

- Navigation groups → directories
- Navigation pages → `.mdx` files
- Nested groups → nested directories
- Single pages (not in a group) → files at that level

```
docs/
├── docs.json                 # Mintlify config (nav, tabs, API settings)
├── getting-started/          # Intro & quickstart
│   └── introduction.mdx
├── product/                  # Product documentation
│   ├── scenario-studio.mdx
│   └── use-cases/            # Nested group
│       └── sales-coaching.mdx
├── developer/                # Developer guides
│   ├── overview.mdx          # Single page at group level
│   ├── troubleshooting.mdx   # Single page (not nested)
│   ├── starters.mdx          # Single page (not nested)
│   ├── integration/          # "Integration" group → directory
│   │   ├── iframe.mdx
│   │   ├── api.mdx
│   │   └── authentication.mdx
│   ├── nextjs-starter/       # "Next.js Starter" group → directory
│   │   ├── overview.mdx
│   │   ├── project-structure.mdx
│   │   └── ...
│   └── flask-starter.mdx     # Single page (not a group)
├── api-reference/
│   ├── overview.mdx
│   ├── endpoints/
│   │   └── scenarios/
│   │       └── list-scenarios.mdx
│   └── openapi.json
└── public/                   # Static assets (logos, favicon)
```

### Why This Matters

- Easier to find files when they match sidebar structure
- Prevents broken links when navigation changes
- Clearer mental model for contributors

## MDX Guidelines

### Formatting Rules

- **Line length**: Keep under ~100 characters
- **No JSX artifacts**: Never use `{" "}` - causes rendering issues
- **Inline exports only**: Mintlify doesn't support importing from `.ts` files

```mdx
<!-- ✅ Correct: inline export -->

export const items = [{ title: "Item 1" }];

<!-- ❌ Wrong: external import -->

import { items } from "./data.ts";

;
```

### Frontmatter

```yaml
---
title: "Page Title" # Main heading
sidebarTitle: "Sidebar Name" # Optional: different name in sidebar
description: "Brief description"
---
```

### Mintlify Components

````mdx
