```

## docs.json Key Settings

### Tabs

```json
"tabs": [
  { "tab": "Documentation", "groups": [...] },
  { "tab": "API Reference", "groups": [...] }
]
```

### API Configuration

```json
"api": {
  "openapi": "api-reference/openapi.json",
  "playground": { "display": "interactive" },
  "mdx": {
    "server": "https://api.toughtongueai.com/api/public",
    "auth": { "method": "bearer" }
  }
}
```

### Navigation

Pages must be listed in `navigation` to appear in sidebar.
**Directory structure must match navigation paths.**

## Content Guidelines

### Do's

- ✅ Be concise - no filler content
- ✅ Use action-oriented titles ("Create Scenario" not "Scenario Creation")
- ✅ Add `<Note>` for beta features: "Beta: This feature is under development"
- ✅ Link to related pages
- ✅ Use code examples sparingly

### Don'ts

- ❌ Don't hallucinate features (e.g., made-up rate limits)
- ❌ Don't add unnecessary sections
- ❌ Don't exceed ~100 char line length
- ❌ Don't use `{" "}` in MDX
- ❌ Don't import from external TypeScript files

